  "title": "Get search request for backend usage",
  "body": "Sometimes we want to be able to create the client compatible search query so that we can replicate the search with any API client. For example, this can be used for making a \"download all results\" feature, that will rely on doing a browse all on the backend side.\r\n\r\n### Proposed API\r\n\r\n```js\r\nvar query = helper.getHitsQueryParameters();\r\nvar browser = client.browseAll(query);\r\n```",
